492
00:27:19,889 --> 00:27:21,474
Ngài Gatsby?

493
00:27:21,641 --> 00:27:22,475
<i>♪ Sweet baby
Anh yêu ơi</i>

494
00:27:22,642 --> 00:27:23,601
Đi nào.

495
00:27:23,935 --> 00:27:25,145
