524
00:28:27,248 --> 00:28:28,708
<i>♪ Killed nobody
hại ai hết</i>

525
00:28:28,875 --> 00:28:30,168
<i>♪ So we gonna dance
Ta sẽ khiêu vũ</i>

526
00:28:30,335 --> 00:28:32,086
<i>♪ Until we drop
