1950
01:51:29,517 --> 01:51:30,476
Sao anh có thể?

1951
01:51:30,643 --> 01:51:31,561
Sao anh làm thế?

1952
01:51:31,728 --> 01:51:32,729
Cậu nói bé thôi.

1953
01:51:32,896 --> 01:51:33,856
